'''SM-1''' was a sentient controlled [[Droid/Legends|droid]] onboard the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Starship/Legends|ship]] [[Steadfast (carrier)|''Steadfast'']], and was used to search destroyed vessels for traps before being [[Scavenger/Legends|salvaged]]. In [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]] SM-1 was one of the droids involved in the finding of an operational datacore on the [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] ''[[Gnisnal]]'' that allowed for the discovery of the [[Black Fleet]].

SM-1's handler was [[Makki]].

